reforms.name: Heavenly Kingdom of the Great Mingshun

E005.title: Beijing Treaty
E005.description: The Japanese refused our offer and completely annexed Sakhalin to themselves.

E002.title: Beijing Treaty
E002.description: It is time to return to negotiations with the Japanese on the establishment of peaceful relations and the return of Northern Sakhalin.
E002.description1: You begin to negotiate with Japan.

E003.title: Beijing Treaty
E003.description: The Soviet delegation in Beijing proposes that we withdraw our troops from Northern Sakhalin in exchange for economic concessions in the region.
E003.description1: You are withdrawing your troops from Northern Sakhalin.

E001.title: Merger of Two Powers
E001.answer2: Let everything remain as it is!
E001.description: The White Army is defeated. Now that Soviet power has been established in the Far East, isn't it time for us to unite with the Far Eastern Republic?
E001.description2: Far Eastern Republic remains your union republic.

E004.title: Beijing Treaty
E004.description: The Japanese agreed to our proposal.

E006.title: Colony Expansion
E006.description: Our Emperor has decided to annex the northern parth of the island to us!
